<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">藍牙</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">藍牙是一種無線傳輸協定，讓您可以連接許多不同類型的裝置到電腦上。藍牙常被使用在頭戴式耳機以及輸入裝置（如滑鼠和鍵盤）。您也可以用藍牙<span class="link"><a href="bluetooth-send-file.html" title="傳送檔案至藍牙裝置">在裝置間傳送檔案</a></span>，例如：從您的電腦傳送檔案到您的手機。</p>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner"><div class="region">
<div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="bluetooth-turn-on-off.html" title="開啟或關閉藍牙"><span class="title">開啟或關閉藍牙</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">啟用、停用電腦上的藍牙裝置。</span></a></div>
<div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="sharing-bluetooth.html" title="Control sharing over Bluetooth"><span class="title">Control sharing over Bluetooth</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">Bluetooth file sharing and receiving options.</span></a></div>
<div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="bluetooth-send-file.html" title="傳送檔案至藍牙裝置"><span class="title">傳送檔案至藍牙裝置</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">在手機等藍牙裝置間分享檔案。</span></a></div>
<div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="bluetooth-connect-device.html" title="將您的電腦連接至藍牙裝置"><span class="title">將您的電腦連接至藍牙裝置</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">配對藍牙裝置。</span></a></div>
<div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="bluetooth-remove-connection.html" title="移除藍牙裝置的連接"><span class="title">移除藍牙裝置的連接</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">從藍牙裝置清單內移除裝置。</span></a></div>
